It is a smoke free hotel, but guests tend to sneak smokes in stairwells and in the under building parking, staff does not police this.	The hotel is located about 2 miles from the "downtown action"- but the ease of free parking onsite and sight-seeing trolley that stops there frequently make up for that small inconvenience.	There is free parking though it is too far to walk to the beaches and Duval St. from the hotel.	Free parking, no hidden extra charge, they gave us a second cocktail for free at the swimming-pool bar.